{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-03057/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-03057"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:30:57"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tracking, pan"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man examines a box on a shelf, putting on and taking off his glasses."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-03057","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-03057"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/canvas/1/3a84734a-6438-4dc4-b4f8-caed3a6c1828","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:45:30.304Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds’s house is once again shot to resemble a castle or dungeon. Here, the dressmaker enters a storage space to pull out a secret. As Mark Kermode notes in his review of the film, there are echoes of fairy tales throughout the film. Here, viewers might recall Bluebeard (kermodeandmayo, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW167255842 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PhRCSiNNE6o\"><u>Phantom Thread reviewed by Mark Kermode</u></a>”). In an interview with Terry Gross, PTA acknowledges the fairy tale influence and also mentions Beatrix Potter’s “The Tailor of Gloucester” and the stories of M. R. James (Xixax TV, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW167255842 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dJYazfgvQGU\"><u>PHANTOM THREAD - AUDIO</u></a>\"). On the Potter connection, see also Shackleton’s “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW167255842 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=au7NMfNWrhE\"><u>PHANTOM THREAD Q&amp;A</u></a>.”&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1144.8543689320388,165.63106796116503,448.9320388349513,375.9223300970874"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/canvas/1/decaccef-54f0-449a-a8fe-48018d87d509","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:45:45.719Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The camera lingers on Reynolds’s eyes as seen through a crack between the shelves and boxes. This shot underscores the significance of his aesthetic vision, which he wields to craft his dresses and to give structure to his life.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03057/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:509.5145631067961,237.08737864077668,375.9223300970874,242.33009708737868"}}}]}]}]}